SUMMARY:Letting Go Isn't Avoidance: How To Be Done with the Past
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nWhat does it take 
 to really get a fresh new start on your life? This is an incredibly vital 
 profound skill that society did not teach you and few people understand. T
 he answer goes way beyond traditional self-improvement or manifestation te
 chniques. Forgiveness and deserving are just the beginning. Old traumas ne
 ed to be healed\, as the many old lies\, denials\, and addictions are reve
 aled. You see\, this is the so-called ascension time\, when the old world 
 is dying and the opportunity to create a new world must be consciously rea
 lized by each individual. Seize the day! And make all of your dreams come 
 true. Humanity is on the brink of self-destruction exactly because it is r
 eady to claim its divine creatorship in time to fix everything. Learn how 
 to master your own future choices\, so you can live happily ever after in 
 the communities where you belong to thrive.\n\nEach consciousness has alwa
 ys generated its own reality\, but the overlapping of collective beliefs m
 ade it look like there was one cruel world to compete within and fight ove
 r. Now that we’re at the end of that tragic group narrative\, the realit
 ies are splitting to show which people still want to end the world in war 
 and ecological disaster\, and which people are reaching for peace and heal
 ing. Folks who fear conspiracies will lash out recklessly as they try to e
 scape the matrix\, break the system\, and punish whatever trapped them in 
 suffering. The problem is that the one who gets punished and judged is the
  self. It’s a tall order to shift the whole paradigm\, and it becomes ea
 sy when you let the living loving Universe be your friend. Life wants you 
 to succeed with the new spiritual solutions that are real. The old false p
 romises of negative belief systems will keep you in self-sabotage\, with p
 lenty of miserable companions to keep you company.\n\nJoin us this Sunday 
 March 29\, 2026 for a free life-changing talk on how to change your whole 
 approach to life. You’ll learn how to work with your own higher self tha
 t has all the answers you’ll ever need\, and how to leave the negative s
 urvivalism that made Earth 1.0 such a traumatic experience.\n\nWelcome! Ou
 r Inner Selves Mastery spiritual support group is free online every Sunday
  11am-130pm EDT\, with the last 30 minutes for a guided meditation. If you
  can’t stay you can get the recording. You can signup here for this meet
 ing and visit [www.signupISM.com](http://www.signupISM.com) for all events
 \, newsletter\, videos\, and more.\n\nBest wishes\,\nCarl Johann Schroeder
 \nInner Selves Mastery\nspiritual teaching and coaching\nquick-links at [w
 ww.signupISM.com](http://www.signupISM.com)
