SUMMARY:Free Medieval Combat Training (Durham\, NC) - Broadsword - Armor -
  Rapier
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nLearn the European
  martial art of broadsword and shield\, wearing steel armor. Or maybe Rena
 issance dueling with rapier and dagger is more your style. Beginners welco
 me! No experience necessary. Some loaner armor is available.\n\nRapier ins
 tructor: Percival Aldridge\, OD\, OP\nBroadsword instructor: William of Be
 dford\, KSCA\nAdministrator (KM): Charles Fleming\n*This event is held and
